{"tid":1751670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（下一步行動Post）和你賀","createTime":"2019-11-24T17:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T06:51:37.000Z","uid":72431,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"baf4a02890b675cf9449f45bd858ea18163aab2e","tid":1751670,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:52:29.000Z","msg":"依家就咁睇<br />\n應該係會大勝<br />\n我地上次小規模幫劉江華果d唱小凰姐，純粹自娛，笑下共狗<br />\n我地今次大勝<br />\n我地應該大搞慶祝活動<br />\n英超奪冠咁租巴士巡遊<br />\n或者台灣選贏總統咁慶祝<br />\n唔得就細搞，商場慶賀，好似之前一系列商場唱k活動咁<br />\n開香檳，唱小凰姐，唱榮光，和你非活動聚人就可<br />\n<br />\n行動絕非圍爐打飛機<br />\n目的有二：<br />\n<br />\n1: 選舉當成公投，確認得到香港絕大多數民意授權，支持之前既勇武行動，市民絕無割蓆，之前行動係一場改革行動。公投確認香港市民為民主支持者，支持5大訴求，要求2020實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n2:大做國際文宣，令西方國家各個制裁中共民主意案更易通過，試想象下，若果今日民主派大敗，中共就會指責主流民意係和平反暴，大一統，Trump都唔好意思簽法案啦。<br />\n國際文宣重點強調依個選舉係公投，香港市民支持民主，希望2020實行雙普選，履行一國兩制高度自冶承諾。放大個point，國際就易配合做野制裁中共<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n同意就正評，揾搞手book場 book車 下星期六日搞</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c04e83a7c8afe7d67fae0cfb3f23c45aaeb0346","tid":1751670,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:58:40.000Z","msg":"慶祝完記得繼續關注同支援手足"},{"pid":"f653830784c89d3ed26745fd00dc7ff86aab0ac0","tid":1751670,"uid":252292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:00:40.000Z","msg":"完左要一齊救Poly手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ff3c0322df1e9b5435d84fb2f1ed55e75206a5","tid":1751670,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:10:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c3e5b3b3819d94a21f2e95c03197dfdcc59d549","tid":1751670,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:10:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f71ec8ace369cec7d6f63142376ef6846f8b80eb","tid":1751670,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9cac5f2afa2358ab4ced5e37d00b5690c35480a","tid":1751670,"uid":266424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:18:39.000Z","msg":"由今日開始，呢個人血饅頭你已經食左！<br />\n如果你地任何一人唔立刻幫義士，我地發誓<br />\n<br />\n「下次你哋會輸得好慘」"},{"pid":"7619d46da04ad56749f944d4959344f2e7b9f76a","tid":1751670,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:45:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f79db8953c2b6118d8748a91a53cc642b968e0d1","tid":1751670,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:27:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66d8954a0db00e1341bdb2cbd6ff329b0cdac3ed","tid":1751670,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3954db15ba325159890f5f29347f219bf44e9b","tid":1751670,"uid":282455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:12:40.000Z","msg":"即刻親身去 Poly 救人先啦"},{"pid":"e66abeadacda907f35eccee79aa7e92e185b91f4"